  "detailed_description": "After successfully developing a working magnet gun prototype, Maxwell Industrial Research's space lab is attacked! Use the magnet gun to break through obstacles and escape back to earth with the help of your trusty AI companion, Armitage.<br><br>The magnet gun can be used to attract or repel magnetic objects. The player uses this to fight enemies, solve puzzles, and cross platforms.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>5 different environments<br></li><li>Physics-based puzzles<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/995340/extras/d09e1e74db1bc2ff1c4cdd62c8928f9f.poster.avif?t=1551474329\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/995340/extras/d09e1e74db1bc2ff1c4cdd62c8928f9f.webm?t=1551474329\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/995340/extras/d09e1e74db1bc2ff1c4cdd62c8928f9f.mp4?t=1551474329\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></li><li>Intense platforming<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/995340/extras/52f60aa524a2d5120f9f31c5dad44461.poster.avif?t=1551474329\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/995340/extras/52f60aa524a2d5120f9f31c5dad44461.webm?t=1551474329\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/995340/extras/52f60aa524a2d5120f9f31c5dad44461.mp4?t=1551474329\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></li><li>Physics-based fights<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/99